fields.name: Innovation
fields.description: Evaluates the level of innovation incorporated into the project, product, or process.

fields.name: Market potential
fields.description: Assesses the attractiveness and potential of the target market for the project or product.

fields.name: Team expertise
fields.description: Examines the skills, knowledge, and experience of the team executing the project.

fields.name: Execution plan
fields.description: Analyzes the detailed plan and strategy for implementing and accomplishing project goals.

fields.name: Financial viability
fields.description: Gauges the financial feasibility and sustainability of the project.

fields.name: Technology readiness
fields.description: Assesses the readiness and maturity of the technology being employed.

fields.name: Market fit
fields.description: Examines how well the product or service aligns with the needs and demands of the target market.

fields.name: Customer acquisition strategy
fields.description: Evaluates the planned approach for acquiring and retaining customers.

fields.name: Scalability
fields.description: Assesses the potential for the project or product to grow and handle increased demand.

fields.name: Competitive landscape
fields.description: Analyzes the competitive environment and positioning within the industry.

fields.name: Regulatory compliance
fields.description: Ensures adherence to legal and regulatory requirements.

fields.name: Customer feedback
fields.description: Gathers insights from customer interactions and feedback to inform improvements.

fields.name: Strategic partnerships
fields.description: Examines collaborations and alliances that contribute to the project's success.

fields.name: Risks and mitigations
fields.description: Identifies potential risks and outlines strategies to mitigate them.

fields.name: Sustainability practices
fields.description: Assesses the project's commitment to environmentally and socially sustainable practices.
